node-nexmoapi
Written by Aaron Blakely <aaron@ephasic.org>
--------------------------------------------------------------------
To 'require' the node-nexmoapi package's Receipt API simply do this:
	var nexmoReceipt = require('nexmoapi').NexmoReceipt;
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Functions:

start:
	starts the receipts server.
	NOTE: it runs on 4032, so http://localhost:4032/receipts

stop:
	stops the receipts server.
